{"tid":2159698,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無名英雄！她被「黎巴嫩大爆炸」震暈　醒來繼續搶救「3位嬰兒」","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:34:29.000Z","uid":153217,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c23d3e1a764bcaac855c6c897f92ba13f2b4e89","tid":2159698,"uid":153217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ASzyXgz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FASzyXgz.gif&h=b0d9dac2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYv2QBW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYv2QBW.jpg&h=20fadfe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月4日，黎巴嫩首都貝魯特（Beirut）發生大爆炸，現場有蕈狀雲騰空而起，場面非常慘烈。這次爆炸波及整座城市，導致130多人死亡、5000多人受傷，約30萬人無家可歸。搜救人員正在努力拯救生還者，其中也有很多讓人感動的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sR7pjuY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsR7pjuY.png&h=7ff0dfd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攝影師Bilal Marie Jawish在聖喬治醫院遇到了一位護士，她抱著3個新生兒坐在一片殘垣斷壁之中，周圍還有幾具遺體，但她表現得非常冷靜。 Bilal詢問後得知，爆炸發生時這名護士正在產房中工作，醫院被爆炸衝擊倒塌時她暈倒了，等她醒來發現自己懷裡抱著3個新生兒。<br />\nBilal說：&ldquo;她非常鎮靜，跟周圍混亂的環境形成鮮明的對比。她的身上似乎有一種神秘的力量，她能用這種力量來拯救那些孩子。在混亂、黑暗之中，人們身上的閃光點才能展現出來，那名護士就是這樣的。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUEfq94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUEfq94.jpg&h=ec2fa214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBBQZvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBBQZvb.jpg&h=a2fa1a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypqFCgS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypqFCgS.jpg&h=bc473e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這次爆炸中，聖喬治醫院至少有4名護士喪生，200多名患者受傷。 Bilal將這些照片po到社群網站上後，很快就引起了網友們的關注，大家都覺得那位護士是一個無名英雄，她抱著孩子的身影太高大，讓人覺得安全感十足！"},{"pid":"6a891e02c3a45b39bf4d1246e3e33e08be5c0ee9","tid":2159698,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"狗官禍國系列"},{"pid":"e7f1ecdeb34d16ad14a501e599da83ab91e258d4","tid":2159698,"uid":153217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"只為分享在世上別人的生活, 人性的光輝"},{"pid":"d1c466f1f44464fbafe2e9216e63e301b1a454f1","tid":2159698,"uid":153217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vnb16k6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnb16k6.jpg&h=ab9633aa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}